<i>noun</i>: 흠모 [흠모], 탄복 [탄ː복], 찬탄 [찬ː탄], 존경심 [존경심], 존경 [존경], 예찬 [예찬], 숭배 [숭배], 경탄 [경탄], 감탄 [감ː탄], 감복 [감ː복] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>흠모 [흠모]</dt><br>
<dd>admiration; adoration</dd><br>
<dd>기쁜 마음으로 존경하고 마음속 깊이 따름.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of respecting someone readily and following him/her sincerely.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>탄복 [탄ː복]</dt><br>
<dd>admiration; being deeply impressed</dd><br>
<dd>매우 감탄하여 마음으로 따름.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being impressed by and following someone, from one's heart.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>찬탄 [찬ː탄]</dt><br>
<dd>admiration; praise</dd><br>
<dd>칭찬하며 감탄함.</dd><br>
<dd>An expression of admiration and awe.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>존경심 [존경심]</dt><br>
<dd>admiration</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사람의 훌륭한 인격이나 행위를 높이고 받드는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>The attitude of thinking highly of and revering the respectable character or behavior of a person.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>존경 [존경]</dt><br>
<dd>admiration</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사람의 훌륭한 인격이나 행위를 높이고 받듦.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of thinking highly of and revering the respectable character or behavior of a person.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>예찬 [예찬]</dt><br>
<dd>admiration</dd><br>
<dd>매우 좋거나 훌륭한 것을 칭찬하며 감탄함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of praising and marvelling at something good or great.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>숭배 [숭배]</dt><br>
<dd>1. admiration</dd><br>
<dd>우러러 공경함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of admiring and respecting someone or something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. worship</dd><br>
<dd>신이나 부처 등의 종교적 대상을 우러러 받드는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of venerating a religious subject such as a god, Buddha, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>경탄 [경탄]</dt><br>
<dd>admiration; wonder</dd><br>
<dd>매우 놀라며 감탄함.</dd><br>
<dd>Being surprised and impressed very much.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>감탄 [감ː탄]</dt><br>
<dd>admiration; wonder</dd><br>
<dd>마음속 깊이 크게 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of feeling positive about something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>감복 [감ː복]</dt><br>
<dd>admiration</dd><br>
<dd>진심으로 크게 감동함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being impressed strongly and sincerely.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>